title: Oprah With Meghan And Harry First Look | "There's A Lot That's Been Lost"
author: CBS
description: Oprah asks Meghan, The Duchess of Sussex, how she feels about the palace hearing her speak her truth on the special. Watch Oprah with Meghan and Harry: A Primetime Special on Sunday, Mar. 7 at 8/7c on CBS.

localize.description: 奥普拉在特别节目中问苏塞克斯公爵夫人梅根，她对皇宫听她说真话的感受。观看奥普拉与梅根和哈里。周日，3月7日在CBS的8/7c黄金时段特别节目。
localize.title: 奥普拉与梅根和哈里的第一眼｜"有很多东西已经失去了"
